    "text": [
        "It is correctly said that Information technology is now changing our lives. Though it has lots of advantages, but we can see that IT outweigh the disadvantages too. This essay will discuss how this field dominates every activities of human life.",
        "Firstly, at home, we are using lots of facilities through it. For example, if we buy some clothes or some household materials, then we can use online shopping. It gives door to door service. This is possible only through IT.",
        "Secondly, however, people get more leisure time than before. For instance, kids are mainly busy with playing video games. Even, the adults also pass their leisure time by chatting with another. In this way, technology can do a lot in human's life.",
        "Moreover, in work field  also, IT dominates everyone. As, for example, in offices, everything important is to be stored in computer. All records, data etc. are keep in computer. Using the internet, everyone can browse anything whatever they want. Thus, it can said that without IT, nothing is possible.",
        "Meanwhile, the benefits of IT outweigh the disadvantages. Though it has great demand at our home, free time and work fields, it has disadvantages also. Using IT more oftenly, it creates addiction. Inspite of this, everyone in dependent on it. It creates lots of health problems amongst the individuals. Major health problem by using it is obesity.Excessive use of it can create distress, anxiety etc. of the individuals.",
        "To sum up, it is said that despite the Information technology helps in every spheres of human life, indeed, it has lots of limitations too. So, we use it as per our convinience and we should not overuse it."
